CBRE and CG Property as the exclusive agents invite you to secure your new logistics facility in the Barracks at Metroplex Estate within the highly sought-after Wacol precinct.

Located within the estate is the National Head office for Volvo Trucks, Aggreko and All Class Equipment.

The estate also has the ability to house users up for purpose-built facilities from 3,500sqm* to 50,000sqm* in one line.

To further discuss, please contact the exclusive marketing agents from CBRE and CG Property.
